  <title>libconfig-&libconfig-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Libconfig is a simple library for processing structured configuration
      files which are more readable than XML and are type-aware, so it is not
      necessary to do string parsing in application code. Libconfig is very
      compact which makes it well-suited for memory-constrained systems.
    </para>

